    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Graphical Siege is an action fps where you will dive into a unique comic book world where each frame is a battlefield. As the player, you will navigate through the different pages, battling hordes of zombies, soldiers, airborne enemies, and other dangers to save a world under the siege of a mad man.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173670/extras/5f176e64bb5f6148727a395f1c98f8df.poster.avif?t=1737773430\" width=800 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173670/extras/5f176e64bb5f6148727a395f1c98f8df.webm?t=1737773430\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173670/extras/5f176e64bb5f6148727a395f1c98f8df.mp4?t=1737773430\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Equipped with a shotgun, you can swap it for a rifle to deal higher damage, but with a slower rate of fire. Multiply your firepower with the large head power-up for devastating attacks that turn the tide of battle in your favor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Captivating dynamic gameplay, and visually striking comic book aesthetics, &quot;Graphical Siege&quot; delivers an adrenaline-fueled FPS experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173670/extras/e887a4bb9183fdeb3478d8e33663fe2d.poster.avif?t=1737773430\" width=800 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173670/extras/e887a4bb9183fdeb3478d8e33663fe2d.webm?t=1737773430\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3173670/extras/e887a4bb9183fdeb3478d8e33663fe2d.mp4?t=1737773430\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
